text: Popsie was a Swedish pop girl group consisting of Cecilia Lind, Sandra Pettersson, Angelica Sanchez and Katarina Sundqvist. Between 1997 and 1998 they had several charting songs on the Sverigetopplistan like "Single", "Joyful Life", "Latin Lover", "Rough Enough" and "24Seven". ==Discography== ===Singles=== {| class="wikitable plainrowheaders" style="text-align:center;" |- ! scope="col" rowspan="2"| Title ! scope="col" rowspan="2"| Year ! scope="col" colspan="1"| Peak chart positions ! scope="col" rowspan="2"| Album |- ! scope="col" style="width:3em;font-size:85%;"| SWE |- ! scope="row"| "Joyful Life" | 1998 | 3 | |} ==References== Category:Swedish pop music groups
